WEBVTT

00:04.938 --> 00:08.575
Some time ago, something
crawled or slithered or grew

00:08.576 --> 00:10.043
like a fungus.

00:10.044 --> 00:12.445
Something that started small,

00:12.446 --> 00:14.981
got bigger, lurched like a swamp

00:14.982 --> 00:17.050
thing out of the mud and moist

00:17.051 --> 00:19.152
earth and humid
nights of the delta.

00:19.153 --> 00:22.289
Then it took over the world.

00:22.290 --> 00:30.290
So next time some smartass
horrified by our ham-fisted

00:30.298 --> 00:31.398
foreign policy wonders what good

00:31.399 --> 00:32.598
is America, well, you can always

00:32.600 --> 00:34.934
pipe up that the blues, rock and

00:34.935 --> 00:39.239
roll, R & B, and soul all
came out of this place.

00:39.240 --> 00:43.310
One state, Mississippi.

